Intenta mantenerlo adentro ♪</i>

571
00:31:19,515 --> 00:31:21,640
- Adiós.
- Adiós, Birdy.

572
00:31:21,642 --> 00:31:23,143
- Adiós, Shelly.
- Adiós, Shelly.

573
00:31:26,730 --> 00:31:29,439
¿Por qué ese cigarrillo
se ve tan extraño?

574
00:31:29,441 --> 00:31:31,501
