00:34:30,081 --> 00:34:32,706
♪ Ven, estréllate ♪

616
00:34:32,708 --> 00:34:34,749
♪ En mí ♪

617
00:34:34,751 --> 00:34:37,878
- ♪ Cariño ♪
- ♪ En mí ♪

618
00:34:38,838 --> 00:34:42,048
♪ Entro en ♪

619
00:34:45,512 --> 00:34:50,307
<i>♪ Tocar tus labios
Solo para que yo sepa ♪</i>

620
00:34:50,309 --> 00:34:51,934
<i>♪ En tus ojos ♪</i>

621
00:35:06,992 --> 00:35:08,700
Son unos calcetines increíbles.

622
